title: Issei Takahashi (footballer)
text:
is a <a href="Japanese%20people">Japanese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="JEF%20United%20Chiba">JEF United Chiba</a>.
Career.
Issei Takahashi joined <a href="J2%20League">J2 League</a> club <a href="JEF%20United%20Chiba">JEF United Chiba</a> in 2017.
